&lt;p&gt;A Clinic Prep Clerk is required to work within the Medical Records Library at Doncaster Royal Infirmary.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be confident, articulate, possess good interpersonal skills and be able to work alone or as part of a team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A good standard of education is essential with minimum GCSE O level or equivalent in Maths and English. Typing skills, an equivalent IT qualification or the ability to demonstrate this level through experience is essential.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Due to the nature of the post, you must be accurate, organised and possess excellent communication skills. The work can sometimes be physically demanding.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
